Bugzilla,is,the,bug,tracking,and,reporting,system,created,and,used,by,Mozilla,It,is,also,available,for,use,by,other,projects,and,organizations,The,life,cycle,of,a,bug,also,known,as,workflow,is,customizable,to,match,the,user,s,needs,The,Bugzilla,REST,API,provides,users,with,programmatic,access,Bugzilla,s,service,using,either,JSON,or,JSONP